<hymn_number>151</hymn_number>
<title>Suihlung Muonna</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Albang ka vaihna nuoi simlei ahin,
 Zinmang dogal siel ang a lien;
 Lalpa sau nuom thuong ka tun ma'n,
 Muonna kim him ka nei thei puoi.

[V2]
 Aw, suihlung muonna Lal mang Isu,
 Zinmang dogal lai ah;
 Nau bang ei pui zelin.

[V3]
 2. Nunnawpna ni lopi lenkawl en tieng,
 Sietlei dogal cheng nuoisieh in;
 Lalpa gam nuomah leng hiting,
 Lalpa pakchan zaila sai tiu.

[V4]
 3. Nuoi simlei ah ngabang in leng mahleng,
 Lalpa chawnban zaitha hat chun;
 Dogal lai ah ei pui in tin,
 Gam ninnuom thuong ei tun ina.

[V5]
 4. Lalpa gam nuoma laituol I len tieng,
 Lalpa vanga I thawkna cheng;
 Naubang kah leh luonthi nulna,
 I nunnawpnau pak hung hina.</lyrics>
</song>